movies.title: The Wonderful World of Disney Princess of Thieves
movies.title_english: The Wonderful World of Disney Princess of Thieves
movies.title_long: The Wonderful World of Disney Princess of Thieves (2001)
movies.summary: Story of Robin Hood's daughter Gwyn who takes up his role after he is captured by Prince John. King Richard is dead and his son Philip is the rightful heir, but he is in France and too afraid to face John. Can Gwyn find Philip and convince him to fight John and free her father?

movies.title: Along Came the Devil 2
movies.summary: After receiving an unsettling voicemail, Jordan (Wiggins) returns home, looking for answers, only to find her estranged father and even more questions. A demonic force has attached itself to the town and no one is safe. The only one who seems to know anything is the small town's Reverend.

movies.title: A Street Cat Named Bob
movies.summary: Based on the international best selling book. The true feel good story of how James Bowen, a busker and recovering drug addict, had his life transformed when he met a stray ginger cat.

movies.title: Dhuruvangal Pathinaaru
movies.summary: Deepak is an retired police officer. He meets an young man who is interested in joining IPS. The young guy asks about the case of a mystry killer in which deepak lost his leg and his career. Thus he explains about the unsolved mystry case. But in the end the case is solved by the young man, and deepak meets his ultimate end.
